title: Jamie Lee
itunes:title: Jamie Lee
description:
Comedian Jamie Lee (Crashing, Ted Lasso) comes on Good For You to talk about her amazing Netflix series The Wedding Coach and she and Whitney discuss Whitney's hideous dream dresses, nightmare best man speeches, and the biggest mistakes brides make (hint: getting married).  We also marvel at Jamie's incredible ass.
